    <text>
        <front>
            <div type="summary">
                <p>
                   A letter written by <persName>Vita</persName> to <persName>Leonard</persName> about reprinting <title>Pepita</title> and questioning the possiblity to make minor alterations beforehand
                </p>
            </div>
        </front>
        <body>
            <div type="letter">
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <placeName>
                             Sissinghurst Castle, Kent
                        </placeName>
                        <date when="1946-04-08">
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>
                            <persName> Leonard </persName>
                        </addrLine>
                        <addrLine>
                            <!-- recipient's address (add <addrLine>s as required) -->
                        </addrLine>
                    </address>
                    <salute>
                         My Dear <persName>Leonard</persName>,
                    </salute>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    I was very glad to hear that you were
                    not giving up the Press and also that you are
                    hoping to reprint my books before very long.
                    I think I should like <title>Pepita</title> done first. Would
                    you be resetting the type? If so I should like
                    to correct some misprints and also to make a few
                    minor alterations.
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>
                         Yours ever,
                    </salute>
                    <signed> <persName>Vita</persName> </signed>
                    <seg>
                        <!-- post scriptum -->
                    </seg>
                </closer>
            </div>
